and experience to the act of creation.

171
00:14:48,015 --> 00:14:51,576
Let's start...
with my passion--

172
00:14:51,652 --> 00:14:53,620
chili peppers.

173
00:14:53,688 --> 00:14:56,248
They come
from the Americas...

174
00:14:56,324 --> 00:15:00,021
