It smells like a vegetable?

184
00:15:28,222 --> 00:15:30,156
[ All Laughing ]

185
00:15:30,224 --> 00:15:34,024
So, now here's my favorite--
malagueta pepper.

186
00:15:34,095 --> 00:15:36,359
Don't be fooled
by its tiny size.

187
00:15:36,430 --> 00:15:39,092
